CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 24, 1964, pg. 9 reads: Exercising - Three of the Slenderettes go through some of their exercises at one of their weekly meetings at the Kay Boys Club. Left to right: Marion Smith, Bessie Collins and Minnie Hall. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Slenderettes members Marion Smith, Bessie Collins, and Minnie Hall, going through exercise routine during weekly meeting in Kay Boys Club
